data.description: Step into this impressive executive two-story home, adorned with a meticulously manicured lawn and a charming covered porch area. Boasting 5 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, 3 car garage, spacious laundry room, and a bonus room, this residence offers a perfect blend of functionality and elegance. The journey begins in a spacious foyer with cathedral-style ceilings, leading to a bright formal dining room and an open living space with easy access to the gourmet kitchen.    Inside, discover a kitchen upgraded to perfection, featuring dual commercial-quality ovens, an eat-in cafe, and a living room bathed in natural light. Neutral interior paint tones, abundant windows, tall ceilings creating a bright, and airy atmosphere. The kitchen, a focal point of luxury, presents an oversized island, exquisite granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a large, custom built walk-in pantry.    Through the sliding glass doors, it opens to a covered lanai with views of the well oversized fenced in backed yard. You have the option to expand the outdoor space for additional entertainment possibilities.     On the second floor, discover primary suite providing privacy and offers a splendid view of the backyard and lake. The bathroom is a personal retreat with double sinks separated by a large bathtub, a private commode area, a spacious walk-in shower and a generous sized walk-in closet.  Also, on the second floor is the other three bedrooms as well as an open room suitable for various uses—game room, office, or an additional living room.     This beautiful home is nestled in a quiet and exclusive subdivision, with walking access to the community's resort-style pool, recreational facility, and gym. Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, daycares, and top-rated schools, this gem invites you to explore what could ultimately be your dream home.
